Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒落魄到讓你擔心的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫助惡魔之子是一種罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但形勢所迫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霧隱流魔劍技 蛇腹化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛇牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黃道減滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
