Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.32,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What is Wired Life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.86,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無法逃避之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.86,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}逃れられないなんて
